     Hello All!

     I hate to have to pass this on but I was worried when Doug didn't
     respond to John Souvestre's message about the FidoNews this Monday.
     :(  Here is the message as posted in FN_SYSOP.  Me and Doug had
     gotten close since he selected me to take over the FidoNews in his
     absence back in April and then he ended up not having to have
     surgery but had a balloon angioplasty instead.  I just hate the
     news that another of our dear FidoNet friends has died. :(

     By: BOBBY QUEEN
     ~~~~~~~~~~

     In writing this letter seems to be one of the hardest things I have
     to do. This is let you know that  Doug Myers  passed away on
     September. 17, 2000  Sunday at approximately 8 P.M. in his sleep. I
     know this is a great loss to our Fidonet Community.

     His funeral will be at Fort Indiantown Gap just outside of
     Harrisburg, Pa. The Funeral will be on Thursday  Sept 28, 2000 at
     12:30 P.M.  If anyone is interested in attending you must be at
     Fort Indiantown Gap by 12:15P.M.

     Doug will be buried with Military Honors. Any questions please feel
     free to netmail me at 1:270/911  or email me at john@9-1-1.org

            John
       Harrisburg, Pa.
     ~~~~~~~~~

     I still don't know what to say other than I am heart broken and
     confused at the suddeness of it all.  The good part is he
     apparently passed away quietly in his sleep.  I must assume no pain
     as I have no other information.

     I may well be unavailable 28 SEP.  I am trying to rapid-fix a
     schedule so I can get up to PA from here for his funeral.  No
     promises that I can, but I will *try*.

