     in the eyes.  (count of 5 at slow pace) then drop salute and
     gracefully drop to one knee while bringing the flag to the fore on
     2 outstretched hands.

     " Ms/Mr/David/{insert name of person recieving flag}, On behalf of
     a grateful nation, The {insert branch served in}, and the President
     of the United States, we present to you this flag in honor of
     {insert name/rank} faithful service"

     Rise slowly and salute.

     The 21 gun salute (3 sets from 7 people) follows during the salute
